title: A Wrench In The Works (10 Song Dystopian Synthwave Pack)
description: This package consists of 10 tracks in electronica/dark synthwave/ambient genres with loop files.
longDescription:
A Wrench In The Works is a darkwave/dark synthwave themed electronica album. This music pack is made out of 10 songs which have been written in the same key mostly to provide developers and other artists to be able to capture smooth transitions between scenes and the songs. These 10 tracks' themes and genres can be splitted into:


  1. 4 Action Theme
  2. 2 Chase Theme
  3. 2 Investigation Theme
  4. 1 Stealth Theme
  • 1 Ambient Theme
  • Ambient, BGM, Dark Synthwave, Synthwave


You can watch the album trailer on Youtube by following this link.


Total album duration: 36 Minutes

Does Loop: Some*

  • Your Digital Footprint (Investigation Theme)*
  • Unknown (Hideout Theme)*
  • Looking For A Trace (Investigation Theme 02)*

Loop Files: Available & Provided

CUE Files: Available & Provided
